<subSubSection id="B88331D9FF9FFF68B5E63FD023580502" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="F0266252FF9FFF68B5E63FD023580502" blockId="5.[136,1451,1199,1334]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">
<bibRefCitation id="94081FA3FF9FFF68B5E63FD0215004FE" author="Ducke, W. A." box="[136,290,1199,1226]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" pagination="728 - 729" refId="ref7464" refString="Ducke, W. A. (1932) Especes nouvelles de plantes de l'Amazonie bresilienne. Bulletin du Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle 4 (6): 728 - 729." type="journal article" year="1932">Ducke (1932)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName id="379919D1FF9FFF68B4F73FCF227C04FD" box="[409,526,1199,1225]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Eperua" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oleifera">
<emphasis id="C2EDBE40FF9FFF68B4F73FCF227C04FD" box="[409,526,1199,1225]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">E. oleifera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
listing two of his unnumbered collections and their respective RB old acronym and collection number “H.B.R.J. 
<geoCoordinate id="95AD0495FF9FFF68B4A13FAB224404DA" box="[463,566,1236,1262]" degrees="23.290" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" precision="55" value="23.29">n 23.290</geoCoordinate>
”, and “H.B.R.J. 
<geoCoordinate id="95AD0495FF9FFF68B7813FAB232504DA" box="[751,855,1236,1262]" degrees="20.217" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" precision="55" value="20.217">n 20.217</geoCoordinate>
”. Then, it is unclear which collection is the 
<typeStatus id="2F22DCF0FF9FFF68B02C3FAC25D504D9" box="[1346,1447,1235,1261]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">holotype</typeStatus>
, making it necessary to select a 
<typeStatus id="2F22DCF0FF9FFF68B49F3F8822290525" box="[497,603,1271,1297]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">lectotype</typeStatus>
. The lectotypification made by 
<bibRefCitation id="94081FA3FF9FFF68B6A93F87241B0526" author="Cowan, R. S." box="[967,1129,1271,1298]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" pagination="1 - 45" refId="ref7339" refString="Cowan, R. S. (1975) Monograph of the genus Eperua (Leguminosae: Caesalpinioideae). Smithsonian Contributions to Botany 28: 1 - 45. https: // doi. org / 10.5479 / si. 0081024 X. 28" type="journal article" year="1975">Cowan (1975)</bibRefCitation>
is correct since he chose as 
<typeStatus id="2F22DCF0FF9FFF68B5E63E64209D0501" box="[136,239,1307,1333]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">lectotype</typeStatus>
one of the isosyntypes, Ducke s.n. RB 23290 at R.
</paragraph>
